OL,3,CCalls for LGBTQ+ families in Cumbria
OL,4,Cto adopt a child
OL,6,FThere are calls for more families
OL,7,Fwithin the LGBTQ+ community to foster
OL,8,Fa child in Cumbria.
OL,10,FNew figures have revealed that one in
OL,11,Ffour children in who were adopted in
OL,12,Fthe last three years were adopted by
OL,13,FLGBTQ+ families.
OL,15,FCumbria Adoption works alongside and
OL,16,FWestmorland and Furness Council and
OL,17,Fwithin the last three years 93
OL,18,Fchildren have been adopted with 23
OL,19,Fplaced with LGBTQ+ families.
