OL,6,FThe number of LGBTQ+ families adopting
OL,7,Fa child in Cumbria has doubled since
OL,8,F2018.
OL,10,FRosie Crewdson-Price is a foster
OL,11,Fparent in Cumbria. She believes that
OL,12,Fthere are so many children in the
OL,13,Fcounty who need a loving home and
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FShe said: "I don't think there is a
OL,17,Fstigma now. Years ago, yes there was.
OL,18,FThere is the odd person but for the
OL,19,Fyoung generation it just comes
OL,20,Fnaturally to them now.
