OL,6,F"Years ago it wasn't the done thing,
OL,7,Fnow there are so many children that
OL,8,Fhave the help and support around them
OL,9,Fand if we can help in anyway then we
OL,10,Fwill. Our own sons have girlfriends
OL,11,Fand it is nice that you have a
OL,12,Fvariation of people around you.
OL,14,F"They can help you in any way, shape
OL,15,For form because not everyone is the
OL,16,Fsame."
OL,18,FRosie believes that, although it is
OL,19,Fchallenging, being a foster parent it
OL,20,Fis extremely worthwhile for her.
