OL,3,CCalls for LGBTQ+ families in Cumbria
OL,4,Cto adopt a child
OL,6,FShe said: "I am not going to lie, it
OL,7,Fis demanding. If your heart is in it
OL,8,Fand if you want to help those children
OL,9,Fbecause they come first at the end of
OL,10,Fthe day. It is demanding but the
OL,11,Frewards that you get outweigh it, I
OL,12,Fthink.
OL,14,F"All they basically want is to be
OL,15,Floved, cared and fed. They want a nice
OL,16,Fhome and to be able to go to school
OL,17,Feveryday."
