OL,6,FHer partner Claire explains the
OL,7,Ffeelings she gets being a foster
OL,8,Fparent. She said: "They just want to
OL,9,Fbe loved, wherever that love comes
OL,10,Ffrom they accept that love. It is nice
OL,11,Fto know that you are giving that child
OL,12,Fa start and they love you back.
OL,14,F"You do get the reward."
OL,16,FLaura Worthington from Cumbria
OL,17,FFostering explains the need for more
OL,18,Ffoster carers to step forward in the
OL,19,Fcounty.
