OL,6,FShe said: "There has been a shortage
OL,7,Ffor quite some time so we are putting
OL,8,Fthis out to the LGBT community because
OL,9,Fwe are looking for lots more foster
OL,10,Fcarers.
OL,12,F"We have never discriminated but I
OL,13,Fthink what we found as well was what
OL,14,Fwe learned from our current foster
OL,15,Fcarers and adopters who are part of
OL,16,Fthe LGBT community.
